Adds Dynamic DNS (DDNS) support for the Kea DHCP server.

Manages the kea-dhcp-ddns daemon configuration including TSIG keys,
forward and reverse DNS zones, and per-subnet DDNS policy settings.

Integrates with the core Kea DHCP plugin via the plugins_run() hook
mechanism to inject DDNS parameters into kea-dhcp4.conf.

WWW: https://github.com/opnsense/plugins
